# Strapi v5 Project

## Context

- This is a Strapi v5 application
- Database: SQLite
- Language: JavaScript (no TypeScript)

## Requirements

- Keep answers short and concise
- Do not create long codes in your replies unless explicitly being told to

## Clean Code Principles

- Stay DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself)
- You probably don't have to write a lot of custom code
- Leverage Strapi's built-in features and APIs before creating custom solutions

